  "detailed_description": "Craft and strategically position defenses to safeguard your home against the perils of a hostile environment.<br>Prepare for the challenge as the world teems with wild beasts and formidable adversaries that emerge under the cover of night.<br>Are you ready to fortify your defenses and brave the untamed wilderness?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Gather vital resources, food & minerals. Embark on an exploration through diverse and unique biomes, <br>unraveling their secrets as you navigate each distinct landscape</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/44beb09ce79cce3c002751f5b276d14a.poster.avif?t=1708179500\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/44beb09ce79cce3c002751f5b276d14a.webm?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/44beb09ce79cce3c002751f5b276d14a.mp4?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Build shelter, and craft items then upgrade your weapons, armor, and <br>other equipment. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/b9ccf2800922ab599c7171e749b3dec6.poster.avif?t=1708179500\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/b9ccf2800922ab599c7171e749b3dec6.webm?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/b9ccf2800922ab599c7171e749b3dec6.mp4?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Battle your way through the lands and fight to survive.<br>Some enemies drop rare resource materials that you will need to <br>upgrade new towers, weapons, & armor.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/f6c3b78719d7d4b2de235dd5792bac34.poster.avif?t=1708179500\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/f6c3b78719d7d4b2de235dd5792bac34.webm?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/f6c3b78719d7d4b2de235dd5792bac34.mp4?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/506a0fef83e008d244ebefcdf2188fbb.poster.avif?t=1708179500\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/506a0fef83e008d244ebefcdf2188fbb.webm?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/506a0fef83e008d244ebefcdf2188fbb.mp4?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/40fe224e7abd961bcafb03e9ddc9c1a6.poster.avif?t=1708179500\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/40fe224e7abd961bcafb03e9ddc9c1a6.webm?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/40fe224e7abd961bcafb03e9ddc9c1a6.mp4?t=1708179500\" 